Uses of TokenTrader in tokentrading
 

Subclasses of TokenTrader in tokentrading
 class GlobalTokenTrader
          This version of TokenTrader implements a global token trader strategy The global policy that we chose to implement is to ensure that gates always have least 3 tokens.
 class NoTokenTrader
          A version of TokenTrader which doesn't trade with any other gates.
 class ProfitTokenTrader
          Trades tokens with the goal of gaining as much profit as possible for a gate In order to maximize the profit of a gate it ensures that a gate always has one token
